OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely
OL,6,Fcloudy this evening with showers, some
OL,7,Fheavy and possibly thundery. Most
OL,8,Fshowers dying out through the night,
OL,9,Fbut a few still likely lingering into
OL,10,Fthe early hours.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA mainly dry and partly cloudy
OL,13,Fmorning. Sunny intervals and showers
OL,14,Ffor the afternoon, the best of the
OL,15,Fsunniest conditions on western coasts.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FRain
OL,18,For showers on Tuesday and Wednesday,
OL,19,Foccasionally heavy at first. Drier on
OL,20,FThursday. Warmer than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
